PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784121523
OL,3,CViolent drug dealer guilty of
OL,4,Cmanslaughter after woman fell to her
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FMs Langdon, 25, was repeatedly
OL,8,Fthreatened and suffered a broken nose
OL,9,Fat the hands of Hassan-Agard, who was
OL,10,Farmed with two machetes.
OL,12,FIn a bid to flee from him, Ms Langdon
OL,13,Ffound a way onto the balcony of the
OL,14,Fflat in Cuckmere Lane, where she fell
OL,15,Fto the ground below.
OL,17,FShe died in hospital the following day.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
