OL,3,CViolent drug dealer guilty of
OL,4,Cmanslaughter after woman fell to her
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FDuring the trial, prosecutors proved,
OL,13,Fdespite nobody witnessing the precise
OL,14,Fmoment Ms Langdon fell, that Hassan-
OL,15,FAgard's "conduct was a significant
OL,16,Fcause of the events which led to her
OL,17,Fdeath".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
