PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784121523
OL,3,CViolent drug dealer guilty of
OL,4,Cmanslaughter after woman fell to her
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FJames Foster, Specialist Prosecutor,
OL,8,Fof the Crown Prosecution Service, said
OL,9,Fshe lost her life because of the
OL,10,F"fear, violence and intimidation"
OL,11,Fcreated by Hassan-Agard.
OL,13,F"He then compounded the suffering of
OL,14,Fthose involved by refusing to seek
OL,15,Femergency help and continuing to
OL,16,Fthreaten and control the other victim
OL,17,Fin the aftermath," he said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
